| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-2491 — Recovery Inhibition (medusa)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 94490d9f-a4d0-546e-ba20-741caa105611"
index=* sourcetype=endpoint*
| where (CommandLine="*recoveryenabled no*" OR CommandLine="*bootstatuspolicy ignoreallfailures*") AND (process="*\bcdedit.exe")
